OL,3,CJersey residents lose around #4.4
OL,4,Cmillion this year to scammers
OL,6,FA Jersey farmer who lost #10,000 after
OL,7,Fhe took a call from someone claiming
OL,8,Fto be his bank is warning islanders of
OL,9,Fsophisticated scamming techniques.
OL,11,FOllie Griggs passed a verification
OL,12,Fcode to a scammer over the phone,
OL,13,Fgiving them access to his bank account
OL,14,Fwhere they drained #10,000.
OL,16,FHe is just one of many islanders
OL,17,Fwho've been scammed out of more than
OL,18,F#4.4 million this year, according to
OL,19,Fthe Jersey Financial Crimes Unit
OL,20,F(JFCU).
