OL,3,CJersey residents lose around #4.4
OL,4,Cmillion this year to scammers
OL,6,FIt's almost a #1 million increase from
OL,7,F2023.
OL,9,FOllie says it only briefly occurred to
OL,10,Fhim that the phone call might have
OL,11,Fbeen a scammer, and he believed they
OL,12,Fwere genuinely calling to help.
OL,14,FThe JFCU say that impersonation is
OL,15,Ftaking the most money off of Islanders
OL,16,Fin total.
OL,18,FOllie explains: "It's made me a lot
OL,19,Fmore cautious, a lot more willing to
OL,20,Fquestion, (and) a lot more willing to
OL,21,Fsay: 'Wait - hang on a second.'
