OL,3,CJersey residents lose around #4.4
OL,4,Cmillion this year to scammers
OL,6,F"I'm just a lot more willing to take a
OL,7,Fstep back, and question, and make sure
OL,8,Fthat I'm doing the right thing."
OL,10,FOllie adds that whilst he feels "a bit
OL,11,Fstupid", he hopes telling his story
OL,12,Fwill make people more aware that
OL,13,Ffraudsters are becoming increasingly
OL,14,Fsophisticated.
OL,16,FHe wants to stop others from becoming
OL,17,Ftargets, particularly over the
OL,18,FChristmas period.
