OL,3,CJersey residents lose around #4.4
OL,4,Cmillion this year to scammers
OL,6,FHis story comes as the Jersey Cyber
OL,7,FSecurity Centre (JCSC) warns that
OL,8,Fshoppers are heavily targeted by
OL,9,Fscammers in the weeks leading to
OL,10,FChristmas.
OL,12,FMatt Palmer, Director of the JCSC,
OL,13,Fsays when people are focused on buying
OL,14,Fgifts online and having a good time
OL,15,Fwith their families, it provides a
OL,16,Fprime opportunity for scammers.
