OL,6,FHe says: "It's very important that we
OL,7,Flook very carefully at what we see
OL,8,Fonline, that we don't click unless we
OL,9,Fare absolutely sure, and that we
OL,10,Fexercise a degree of cynicism and
OL,11,Fcaution.
OL,13,F"Goodwill is not universal, and not
OL,14,Feverybody is Santa Claus."
